00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:39,680
There's not even a comparison which plane you're going to feel more comfortable on.

206
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:46,079
And so I do think the like learning from your mistakes thing is a bit of a feel-good trope that actually has very little substance in reality.

207
00:15:46,079 --> 00:15:57,199
It's it's and it's why as an early career product manager or it's it's why like frankly at any stage of your career when you want to learn you should join a winning team.

