00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:42,720
better process, better, you know, general leadership, uh, hiring and firing.

263
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:52,559
I mean just doing the sort of clean up on aisle 3 that needed to be done even though a lot again a lot of the people in the in the team were quite talented and doing an excellent job of managing their specific domains.

