00:31:29,840 --> 00:31:36,480
And he installs it and he goes in and it dumps him onto an empty screen.

402
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,919
And he's like, "What the [ __ ] is this?

403
00:31:37,919 --> 00:31:38,320
What is this?

404
00:31:38,320 --> 00:31:38,799
What's going on?"

405
00:31:38,799 --> 00:31:39,679
Like,"Hey, wow.

